snippet.title: Five Nights at Candy's 3 Minigame Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
=== READ THE DESCRIPTION PLEASE ===
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Please do not re-upload this video on YouTube or anywhere else, you can do a reaction video or
show the video in your own video, but you can't just re-upload the video with no changes made.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Five Nights at Candy's 3 will feature a wide assortment of minigames, some with importance to the story, and some just for one last bit of fun with the FNAC characters! Or is there more to them? Who knows.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------


The official game page --- http://gamejolt.com/games/five-nights-at-candy-s-3-official/130420

My official Tumblr --- http://the-interdimensional-seeker.tumblr.com/
